Jab tootne lage tere sapne sabhi  
Ya tanha lage bheed mein bhi   
Jab dil ho bhaari, par hasna ho zaroori  
Ya yaadon ki barsaat ho raat bhar puri  

Jab dukh kahe "ab saath nahin chhodunga"  
Aur khushi lage jaise kahin kho chuki  
Jab mehsoos ho duniya mein koi apna nahin  
Aur dil ki aawaaz bhi sunayi na de kahin  

Tab tu lena mera naam ek dua ki tarah  
Main rahunga tere saath ek hawa ki tarah 
